reviewText: A great thriller with a positive social message. Its got action, spy-intrigue, and a steamy love scene!  A fun watch, I recommend!

I hope to see this film be turned into a television show. It has a great message to help those who are less fortunate. We need more people who think like this in our country. We see the lead go on a maddening experience which brings him to an understanding about how he should live his life to help others.
